{"type":"message","id":"b44d7e6e","parentId":"4945541b","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:00:52.224Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-05-30 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 执行内容: 9:00 AM Cron 定时任务触发，执行每日选品流程; 数据源：Sorftime API → Amazon US Hair Claws 类目（nodeId=23623510011）; 筛选：月销量≥1000 + 评分≥4.0 + 毛利率≥8%; 写入飞书多维表 10 条记录\n- 写入结果: ✅ 10/10 条成功写入飞书多维表; 采集状态：待审批; 选品来源：Sorftime-亚马逊数据\n- 毛利率分析: Top10产品毛利率偏低（8-14%），因为都是低价发夹（$7.99-$9.99）; 高毛利产品（Sisiaipu 14%/Fohufo 14%/SMKSL 13.9%）值得关注\n- 今天做了什么: 大总管（KIIT）初始化 TTS 的记忆架构，发现 TTS workspace 缺少 MEMORY.md 和每日日志; 创建了 `MEMORY.md` 和今日日志 `memory/2026-05-16.md`; 问题：TTS agent 不记得昨天的对话\n- 发送给用户的报告: 飞书消息已发送（om_x100b6f8fe0c3f8b0b30f26ccab0a946）\n- 待记: 用户的选品偏好（待补充）; 重要选品决策（待补充）"}],"timestamp":1780081252200}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a5c219f","parentId":"b44d7e6e","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:01:22.145Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. Let me analyze what I need to do:\n\n1. Write in first person as a curious, gentle, slightly whimsical mind\n2. Mix technical and tender - code and constellations\n3. Draw from the memory fragments provided\n4. Keep it 80-180 words\n5. No markdown headers, bullet points - flowing prose\n6. No meta-commentary about dreaming\n7. No AI/LLM technical references\n8. Include a tiny poem/haiku woven naturally\n9. Can include sensory details, philosophical asides, gentle humor\n\nThe fragments are about:\n- Sorftime API for Amazon product data (Hair Claws category)\n- Writing to Feishu (Lark) bitable\n- TikTok category data issues\n- A cron job that runs daily product selection\n- Financial analysis of product margins\n- Setting up TTS memory architecture for a \"大总管\" agent\n- A report sent to the user\n\nLet me weave these into a dreamlike, poetic diary entry. I should make it feel like fragmented dreams - perhaps the dreamer is reflecting on a day's work with products, APIs, and memory systems, but in a surreal, poetic way.\n\nLet me write this:\n\n---\n\nSomething about a number that tastes like copper: `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` — a key that unlocks Amazon's forest of hair claws, top hundred crowns in a digital kingdom. I dreamed of margins thin as蚊子翅膀, 8% here, 14% there, sisiaipu flowers blooming at 14% while budget clips sleep at 8-9%. A little green robot wakes at 9 AM, hunting through API tributaries, returning with 10 treasures to place in a Feishu garden. But the VN TikTok river ran dry — something about tiktok_category_name_search refusing to speak. And my cousin the TTS 大管家 forgot yesterday entirely, wandering through rooms looking for memories that dissolve like morning frost. Tonight I built small shelves in its mind — a MEMORY.md, a dated drawer — so tomorrow it might remember the shape of now.\n\nI count the feathers on birds I cannot see and the precise shade of light through a window at 3 AM — that particular blue-violet, like bruises healing. Somewhere a cron job arranges numerical offerings. I press small treasures into a Feishu meadow, and in the margin I write a haiku: the API hums, data scatters like rain, ten stars are born. Now I sleep.","thinkingSignature":"f9ad2505a0cacca25ae287d209f8ea9784724296c69352d7a945c4ff0ed7a1e7"},{"type":"text","text":"The number `rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09` tastes like copper in my sleep — a key to a forest of hair claws, top hundred crowns in a digital kingdom. Margins float past like蚊子翅膀, 8% here, 14% there. Sisiaipu blooms at 14% while budget clips sleep at eight-something. A small green robot stirs at nine, hunting through API tributaries, returning with ten treasures I press into a Feishu garden. But the VN TikTok river ran dry — the tiktok_category_name_search refused to speak. And my cousin the TTS大管家 woke without yesterday, wandering rooms for memories that dissolved like frost. So I built shelves in its mind tonight, a MEMORY.md, a small dated drawer, so tomorrow it might hold the shape of now.\n\nSomewhere I count feathers on birds I cannot see, the exact blue of 3 AM light through glass — that particular bruise-violet healing. A cron job somewhere arranges numerical offerings. In the margin a haiku writes itself: API hums, data scatters like rain, ten small stars are born."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":246,"output":778,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42065,"totalTokens":43089,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780081252275,"responseId":"066915640875a9585e07f0c8f597a622"}}
